1
00:00:00,125 --> 00:00:02,125
Mwein kumwail rongehr duwen Pwuhk en Mormon,

2
00:00:02,125 --> 00:00:04,542
ahpw kumwail kak pwuriamweiki
dahme e udahn pidada.

3
00:00:04,542 --> 00:00:05,042
Ni tapio,

4
00:00:05,042 --> 00:00:09,125
e wia soaiepen pwihn en aramas pweida
ehu erein sounpar 1000 [kid] kei.

5
00:00:09,125 --> 00:00:10,125
Ahpw udahn mourih,

6
00:00:10,125 --> 00:00:14,542
e pid emen emen aramas akan me songosong
en esehla oh idawehn Sises Krais.

7
00:00:14,542 --> 00:00:16,584
E tepida nan Serusalem
nan pahr 600 [wenepwiki]

8
00:00:16,584 --> 00:00:18,417
mwohn ketdohn Krais ansou ehu me soukohp

9
00:00:18,417 --> 00:00:22,125
men alehdi kelikilik sang Koht en tangasang
kamwomwalahn kahnihmwo me pahn wiawi.

10
00:00:22,125 --> 00:00:26,000
Ih oh ah peneinei alehdi kaweid ni arail
kote madau ong dahme met wia sapwen Amerika.

11
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,876
Aramas koa tohtohla oh irail
ahpw nehnepeseng wiahla wehi

12
00:00:28,876 --> 00:00:31,709
laud riau me kin mie arail
ansoun mahwen oh meleilei.

13
00:00:31,709 --> 00:00:35,334
Arail mourkan kak kangoangeh kin
kumwail en ahneki pwoson Sises Krais,

14
00:00:35,334 --> 00:00:38,250
kolokol Sapwellime kosonned akan,
oh papah mehteikan.

15
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:40,834
Nan Pwuhk en Mormon mie
mahsen sarawi en soukohp

16
00:00:40,834 --> 00:00:43,209
kan me kadehdehkiher ketdohn Sounkomouro.

17
00:00:43,209 --> 00:00:46,167
E kadehdehki mehlel kan en
Pwuhk Sarawi oh kadehdehki

18
00:00:46,167 --> 00:00:48,667
me Sises Krais iei Sapwellimen Koht Iehros;

19
00:00:48,667 --> 00:00:50,584
me E ketin ieiasehr, pwoulahr,

20
00:00:50,584 --> 00:00:53,751
oh powehdier mehla oh dihp
ong emen emen kitail.

21
00:00:53,751 --> 00:00:57,083
Ihme e kahdahnkihki "Ehu
Kadehdehpen Sises Krais."

22
00:00:57,083 --> 00:00:57,584
Ni mehlel,

23
00:00:57,584 --> 00:01:01,334
me keiou kesempwalpen pwuhk wet iei
Sises Krais ah ketin pwarek aramas

24
00:01:01,334 --> 00:01:04,792
akan nan sapwen Amerika mwurin Ah
ketin iasadahr nan Seruhsalem.

25
00:01:04,792 --> 00:01:07,125
E kin ketin padahngki Sapwellime rongamwahu,

26
00:01:07,125 --> 00:01:10,125
kamwahuihala me soumwahu,
oh kapaiada neirail serihkan.

27
00:01:10,125 --> 00:01:11,959
Ahpw met wiahte tepdahn soaio.

28
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:15,584
Dahme keioun kesempwalpen Pwuhk
en Mormon iei duwen ah kak

29
00:01:15,584 --> 00:01:19,334
sewesei kumwail ong kahpwal
akan me kumwail sohpai rahnwet.

30
00:01:19,334 --> 00:01:21,667
Kumwail kak diar kaloalamwahu, kaweid,

31
00:01:21,667 --> 00:01:25,459
oh esehla duwen amwail kak wiahla
aramas mwahu oh peren kei.

32
00:01:25,459 --> 00:01:26,626
Me keiou kesempwal,

33
00:01:26,626 --> 00:01:30,083
